OL,3,CTree surgeon thought he was 'going to
OL,4,Cdie' during powerline electric shock
OL,6,FA tree surgeon said he thought he "was
OL,7,Fgoing to die" when he suffered a
OL,8,Fpowerful electric shock from an
OL,9,Foverhead line while clearing hedges in
OL,10,FWiltshire.
OL,12,FJoshua Pocknell was working just after
OL,13,Fmidnight on the A3102 near Royal
OL,14,FWootton Bassett when the mobile
OL,15,Flighting tower he was pushing touched
OL,16,Fan 11,000 volt overhead powerline.
OL,26,@nD@cOUoD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
