FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777683790
OL,3,CTree surgeon thought he was 'going to
OL,4,Cdie' during powerline electric shock
OL,6,FThe 26-year-old was seriously injured
OL,7,Fand taken to hospital, where he spent
OL,8,Fthe next five weeks, workplace
OL,9,Fwatchdog the Health and Safety
OL,10,FExecutive (HSE) said.
OL,12,F"My whole body locked and I felt hot
OL,13,Fand cramping," Mr Pocknell said of the
OL,14,Fshock.
OL,16,F"I could hear the electricity in my
OL,17,Fhead and thought I was going to die.
OL,19,F"I hit the floor and passed out, still
OL,20,Fcramping.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@NO]xD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777683790
OL,3,CTree surgeon thought he was 'going to
OL,4,Cdie' during powerline electric shock
OL,6,F"I later discovered a hole had burnt
OL,7,Fthrough my arm and hip all the way to
OL,8,Fthe bone."
OL,10,FMore than two years after the incident
OL,11,Fon January 19 2024, the tree surgeon
OL,12,Fsaid he still experiences
OL,13,F"considerable pain".
OL,15,F"My injuries were complex and
OL,16,Fchallenging and there were five or six
OL,17,Fdifferent surgeons involved in my
OL,18,Ftreatment," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@JO]uD@AOUuD@SO]wD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777683790
OL,3,CTree surgeon thought he was 'going to
OL,4,Cdie' during powerline electric shock
OL,6,F"I still experience considerable pain
OL,7,Fand strange bodily sensations,
OL,8,Fincluding nerve pain and itching.
OL,10,F"This incident has torn the life from
OL,11,Fbeneath me and I don't think I will be
OL,12,Fable to return to the job that I used
OL,13,Fto love."
OL,15,FThe regulator said it investigated the
OL,16,Fincident and found Mr Pocknell's
OL,17,Femployer, Upton Specialised Tree
OL,18,FServices, did not properly plan for or
OL,19,Frisk assess the dangers posed by
OL,20,Foverhead power lines.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
