FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1777683790
OL,3,CTree surgeon thought he was 'going to
OL,4,Cdie' during powerline electric shock
OL,6,FThe firm did not put up barriers or
OL,7,Fprovide training in operating the
OL,8,Fmobile lighting tower.
OL,10,FUpton Specialised Tree Services
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty to the charge of
OL,12,Fbreaching Regulation 14 of the
OL,13,FElectricity at Work Regulations 1989
OL,14,Fby virtue of Regulation 3, the HSE
OL,15,Fsaid, and was fined #60,000 and
OL,16,Fordered to pay #6,237 in costs at
OL,17,FBristol Magistrates' Court on Friday.
OL,19,FHSE inspector Tom Preston said:
OL,20,F"Joshua is lucky to be alive.
OL,26,@|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
